{"tid":2053242,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭若驊：國安法通過後唔可以當街「扑嘢」","createTime":"2020-06-06T06:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T12:06:40.000Z","uid":212626,"like":691,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"5f434f2cacb80a656150e526dd37635689c07fee","tid":2053242,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:10:27.000Z","msg":"主持陳淑薇質疑新聞界和坊間以後不能批評北京和香港政府「即係叫我哋唔好返工啫」，鄭若驊解釋「梗係唔係啦！我哋咁鍾意你哋節目，點可以冇咗你哋嘅節目呢？（但我哋會繼續批評喎）我哋需要有咁嘅平台，客觀理性討論事情係可以嘅。」<br />\n<br />\n至於內地政權在政策上以至執政合法性，記者報道一些人的政治取態會否動輒得咎，她稱要「分清楚」何為討論，顛覆國家政權、用非法手段破壞和推翻一些東西是兩回事，她指香港以至中國制度都有完整法律條文修例，依足程序「冇人話得你錯」，「但當你去街不斷『扑嘢』（指破壞商店）、打人、掟汽油彈，當然唔得啦！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200606/H6T5ZVUQFIISXSMB5NKQE4L2EI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200606%2FH6T5ZVUQFIISXSMB5NKQE4L2EI%2F&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdxwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=563f4e65\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200606%2FH6T5ZVUQFIISXSMB5NKQE4L2EI%2F&h=54c4a2d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200606/H6T5ZVUQFIISXSMB5NKQE4L2EI/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"551069570a9e82f8e7030b5fbbb5e84e9b3dd241","tid":2053242,"uid":173695,"like":432,"dislike":4,"score":428,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:11:38.000Z","msg":"諗錯咗第樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a0af2967e6b57d1eb03e10ac2f2bad7918c3a5","tid":2053242,"uid":141668,"like":356,"dislike":5,"score":351,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:12:09.000Z","msg":"佛光街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a35d9d1c496cc591d4aa27dbab26dcb655509a0","tid":2053242,"uid":31215,"like":205,"dislike":3,"score":202,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:13:18.000Z","msg":"鄭若驊解釋「梗係唔係啦！我哋咁鍾意你哋節目，點可以冇咗你哋嘅節目呢？（但我哋會繼續批評喎）我哋需要有咁嘅平台，客觀理性討論事情係可以嘅。」<br />\n<br />\n左右紅藍綠<br />\n頭條新聞<br />\n通識試題<br />